{subhead}AmigaD And Games{def}
{left}
{pp}
AmigaDE has now several games to its name for example:
{pp}
{fixed}
* Gobbler (Classic Snake Game)
* Art Avenue Puzzles 1 and 2 (Picture slider games)
* Tikino (Colour square cylcing type game)
* Maze Monster (Pacman type game)
* Planet Zed (scrolling shoot em up) The most popular to date!
* Pagan's blobula (arcade puzzler)
* Solitaire
* Amitello (Othello game)
* Batty (Arkanoid game)
* Boxikon (Shape puzzler game like Tetris)
* Convex (marble puzzle game)
* Gems (Digdug type game)
* Last in line (Number boardgame)
* Linea (Marble game)
* Memory (Shape,colour memory game)
* RDToy (Cycledelic pattern generator)
{def}
{left}
{pp}
For more information and to purchase them visit {link http://de.amiga.com/}http://de.amiga.com{end}{p}
You also need the AmigaDE Player.
{pp}